DeFi Protocols: Platforms like Aave and Uniswap have deployed on Base, enabling users to lend, borrow, and trade assets with minimal fees. These protocols mirror traditional financial services but operate without intermediaries.
Stablecoin Transactions: USDC, widely used on Base, serves as a digital dollar for payments and remittances, offering a stable bridge between fiat and crypto economies.
NFTs and Loyalty Programs: Brands could tokenize loyalty points or rewards on Base, allowing customers to trade or redeem them globally, integrating real-world commerce with onchain ecosystems.

